oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Rodriguez Show at Memorial Auditorium (17301)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Rodriguez, Johnny;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on light Brown) announcing the Johnny Rodriguez Show featuring LaCosta and Don Rhodes at the Memorial Auditorium in Spartanburg, South Carolina on February 20. Poster features a metal photoplate of Johnny Rodriguez. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/39510.
